<type>(<scope>): <short summary in present tense>

# --- INSTRUCTIONS ---
# The summary must be brief (maximum 50 characters).
# Leave a blank line if you want to add a more detailed description below.

# --- COMMIT TYPES ---
# feat:     New feature (auth, api, sidebar)
# fix:      Fixes an error/bug (login-error, typo, api-connection)
# ui:       Visual changes, CSS, layouts (colors, mobile-nav, buttons)
# refactor: Code improvements without changing behavior (performance, clean-code)
# ci:       GitHub Actions, deployment, CI/CD (github-actions, deploy)
# security: Security patches or vulnerable libraries (deps, auth-token)
# chore:    Maintenance, package.json, Node (npm, version-bump)
# docs:     Documentation and comments (readme, api-docs)
# ---------------------

